original_title: Défilé de voitures de bébés à la pouponnière de Paris
overview: A long line of nurses pushing carts with their babies enter from the far right, cross a garden in front of the large nursery home, and leave by the close left to the camera. A few toddlers also follow in the same orderly line, along their nurses.
title: Défilé de voitures de bébés à la pouponnière de Paris
